      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Distill meeting notes with PostgreSQL and Telegram hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDistill meeting notes with PostgreSQL and Telegram hands-free. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual conversational ai is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nOn Telegram Event → Collect Raw Text → Extract Structured Fields → All Required Fields Found? → Upsert into PostgreSQL → Merge Review Paths → Stamp Processing Time → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating conversational ai in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google AI API key; Postgres connection; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
